# Azure Deployment Plan: Mathematically Correct Builds

## Goal
Deploy the Mathematically Correct Builds Flask application to Azure Container Apps with full infrastructure provisioning using Bicep and Azure CLI.

## Project Information

**Mathematically Correct Builds**
- **Stack**: Python 3.14 Flask web application
- **Type**: League of Legends item build optimizer with REST API + HTML/CSS/JS frontend
- **Components**: 
  - Flask API backend (main.py)
  - Static web UI (templates/index.html, static/css/main.css, static/js/app.js)
  - Local JSON caching + HTTP caching layers
  - Optional GPU acceleration (Numba CUDA with CPU fallback)
- **Hosting**: Azure Container Apps
- **Containerization**: Dockerfile will be generated during execution

